{"tid":2053379,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"撕爛護照唔等於喪失國籍，正式入紙Renounce先有用","createTime":"2020-06-06T08:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T04:22:25.000Z","uid":201027,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"073fad2fc3644fedd4f5a032a98c58ad3cece863","tid":2053379,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T08:51:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Renunciation of citizenship（退出國籍）</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">撕爛一本旅行證件，就即時唔係該國公民㗎？</span><br />\n情況就如夫婦鬧交，掉晒啲結婚相、結婚證書，但一日未簽離婚協議書，都仲係合法夫妻！<br />\n<br />\n大波Man及一眾藍屍咪再on9，撕爛本過期護照做下戲子，就當效忠支共、港共！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠膽就好似周庭2017年立法會補選前咁，正式交表向退出英國籍，然後公開嗰份文件俾大家睇！<br />\n<br />\n另外，退出國籍要收費嘅，有唔少美國公民為避免全球徵稅，而放棄美國籍，有見及此，美國政府要收USD$2,350先幫公民做退國籍手續<br />\n退出英國籍GBP&pound;372<br />\n退出加拿大籍CAD$100<br />\n退出澳洲籍AUD$205<br />\n喺香港退出支籍比較平，HKD$575<br />\n<br />\n申請退出中国籍網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/chinese_nationality/Application_for_Renunciation_of_Chinese_Nationality.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.immd.gov.hk%2Fhkt%2Fservices%2Fchinese_nationality%2FApplication_for_Renunciation_of_Chinese_Nationality.html&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx2LrBTEyyW%2B%2F%2BTJtsqEcrWg%3D&h=79469d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.immd.gov.hk/hkt/services/chinese_nationality/Application_for_Renunciation_of_Chinese_Nationality.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（各位巴絲退中国籍前，要考慮下，一退咗仲有冇得投票）"},{"pid":"a251ab5a651dc7c956dbb09089e38fa2c0c03d81","tid":2053379,"uid":201027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T08:55:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽聞退出咗係可以恢復</span>"},{"pid":"9c1409a92af6eae7b1917a98d50f119b2dc8fa60","tid":2053379,"uid":51744,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a251ab5a651dc7c956dbb09089e38fa2c0c03d81","tid":2053379,"uid":201027,